-- Language: en_US
insert or replace into EnglishText
    (Tag,                                                     Text)
values
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_COLLEGE_DESCRIPTION",                 "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat land adjacent to a Campus district with a Library.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Gain +1 [ICON_GOVERNOR] Governor Title. +100% Campus district adjacency bonuses in this City. +20% accumulation rate for [ICON_GREATSCIENTIST] Great Scientist Points. Established [ICON_Governor] Governor in this city provide +5% [ICON_Science] Science for each Promotion earned, including the first."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_COLLEGE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",        "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat land adjacent to a Campus district with a Library.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Gain +1 [ICON_GOVERNOR] Governor Title. +100% Campus district adjacency bonuses in this City. +20% accumulation rate for [ICON_GREATSCIENTIST] Great Scientist Points. Established [ICON_Governor] Governor in this city provide +5% [ICON_Science] Science for each Promotion earned, including the first."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_NATIONALEPIC_DESCRIPTION",            "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built adjacent to a Theater Square with an Art Museum or an Archaeological Museum.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+50% [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person points in this city. Provide corresponding yield of three copies from every [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person earned ([ICON_GreatWriter] Great Writers, [ICON_GreatArtist] Great Artists and [ICON_GreatMusician] Great Musicians provide one copy instead)."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_NATIONALEPIC_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",   "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built adjacent to a Theater Square with an Art Museum or an Archaeological Museum.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+50% [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person points in this city. Provide corresponding yield of three copies from every [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person earned ([ICON_GreatWriter] Great Writers, [ICON_GreatArtist] Great Artists and [ICON_GreatMusician] Great Musicians provide one copy instead)."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_CITADEL_DESCRIPTION",                 "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires that you are at War with other Civilizations. Must be built adjacent to an Encampment district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+1 Military policy slot. Provides the same defensive bonuses as the Fort improvement. Grant Walls and Medieval Walls in this City. Promoting a unit does not end that unit's turn. +4 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength for all military units in your territory. All buildings in Encampment districts provide +2 [ICON_Production] Production and +2 [ICON_Culture] Culture. +100% Encampment district Production adjacency bonuses. Military Engineers gets +1 [ICON_MOVEMENT] Movement and +1 build charge."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_CITADEL_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",        "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires that you are at War with other Civilizations[ENDCOLOR]. Must be built adjacent to an Encampment district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+1 Military policy slot. Provides the same defensive bonuses as the Fort improvement. Grant Walls and Medieval Walls in this City. Promoting a unit does not end that unit's turn. +4 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength for all military units in your territory. All buildings in Encampment districts provide +2 [ICON_Production] Production and +2 [ICON_Culture] Culture. +100% Encampment district Production adjacency bonuses. Military Engineers gets +1 [ICON_MOVEMENT] Movement and +1 build charge."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_TEMPLE_DESCRIPTION",                  "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires that you must have founded a Religion with at least 3 Cities following it. Must be built adjacent to a Holy Site district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Provide +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and [ICON_SCIENCE] Science to [ICON_GREATWORK_RELIC] Relics in this city. Every city of other Civilizations following your Religion provides +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism to [ICON_GREATWORK_RELIC] Relics in this city; doubled if is [ICON_CAPITAL] Capital of other Civilizations."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_TEMPLE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",         "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires that you must have founded a Religion with at least 3 Cities following it.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built adjacent to a Holy Site district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Provide +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and [ICON_SCIENCE] Science to [ICON_GREATWORK_RELIC] Relics in this city. Every city of other Civilizations following your Religion provides +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism to [ICON_GREATWORK_RELIC] Relics in this city; doubled if is [ICON_CAPITAL] Capital of other Civilizations."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_THEMEPARK_DESCRIPTION",               "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires 4 Cities with Entertainment Complex or Waterpark districts. Must be built on a flat tile adjacent to an Entertainment Complex district. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Entertainment Complex or Water Park districts adjacent to Wonders provide +10% [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and [ICON_GOLD] Gold. Entertainment Complex, Water Park districts and each building in them provide +100% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism to Wonders in their city. Pastures, Camps, Plantations and Lumber Mills provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Zoo. Fishing Boats provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Aquarium."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_THEMEPARK_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires 4 Cities with Entertainment Complex or Waterpark districts.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on a flat tile adjacent to an Entertainment Complex district. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Entertainment Complex or Water Park districts adjacent to Wonders provide +10% [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and [ICON_GOLD] Gold. Entertainment Complex, Water Park districts and each building in them provide +100% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism to Wonders in their city. Pastures, Camps, Plantations and Lumber Mills provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Zoo. Fishing Boats provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Aquarium."),

    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_IRONWORKS_DESCRIPTION",               "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Improve 4 Strategic Resources in your empire. Must be built adjacent to Industrial Zone. Each type of Bonus Resource improved by Mine or Quarry provides +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +2 [ICON_GREATENGINEER] Great Engineer Points to all Cities within 9 tiles. Each type of Strategic Resource in this city provides +2 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +2 [ICON_GREATSCIENTIST] Great Scientis Points to all Cities within 9 tiles."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_IRONWORKS_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Improve 4 Strategic Resources in your empire.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built adjacent to Industrial Zone. Each type of Bonus Resource improved by Mine or Quarry provides +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +2 [ICON_GREATENGINEER] Great Engineer Points to all Cities within 9 tiles. Each type of Strategic Resource in this city provides +2 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +2 [ICON_GREATSCIENTIST] Great Scientis Points to all Cities within 9 tiles."),

    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_DESCRIPTION",                    "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes. Must be built on land tile adjacent to a Commercial Hub. Commercial Hub of this city receive +100% adjacency bonus. Banks provide +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. Stock Exchanges provide +4 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",           "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on land tile adjacent to a Commercial Hub. Commercial Hub of this city receive +100% adjacency bonus. Banks provide +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. Stock Exchanges provide +4 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_CORP_DESCRIPTION",               "Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes. Must be built on land tile adjacent to a Corporation. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your Corporations provide +200% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and +20% [ICON_Gold] Gold to their city. [ICON_GreatWork_Product] Products provide double yields in Cities with a Stock Exchange. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_CORP_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on land tile adjacent to a Corporation. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your Corporations provide +200% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and +20% [ICON_Gold] Gold to their city. [ICON_GreatWork_Product] Products provide double yields in Cities with a Stock Exchange. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),

    ("LOC_GOSSIP_SOURCE_NAT_AIRPORT",                         "Stewardesses at the International Airport learn that "),
    ("LOC_VIZSOURCE_NAT_AIRPORT",                             "The International Airport is complete"),
    ("LOC_VIZSOURCE_ACTION_NAT_AIRPORT",                      "Construct the International Airport"),

    ("LOC_HD_NAT_AIRPORT_CORP_ADD",                           ""),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_AIRPORT_DESCRIPTION",                    "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat terrain.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]{LOC_HD_NAT_AIRPORT_CORP_ADD}+3 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Route capacity. Improvements unlocking tourism performance with Flight in Cities with Airport districts and/or the International Airport wonder provide +100% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. International [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes to or from this City provide you with Specialty Districts yields as if this City is the destination; this bonus is doubled if the City has an Airport district and/or the International Airport wonder. Provides an additional level of [ICON_VISLIMITED] Diplomatic Visibility to all Civilizations."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_AIRPORT_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",           "Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat terrain.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]{LOC_HD_NAT_AIRPORT_CORP_ADD}+3 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Route capacity. Improvements unlocking tourism performance with Flight in Cities with Airport districts and/or the International Airport wonder provide +100% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. International [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes to or from this City provide you with Specialty Districts yields as if this City is the destination; this bonus is doubled if the City has an Airport district and/or the International Airport wonder. Provides an additional level of [ICON_VISLIMITED] Diplomatic Visibility to all Civilizations.");

